                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260914-354-off1991 t18260914-354-crimeloc1993"></join> - I fell asleep; I pulled off my hat, and put it behind me - a gentleman came and said it was gone; I then saw the prisoner running away with it; I saw it thrown away afterwards, but cannot say that he threw it - I had seen him with it.</p>
